City Hall will be lit in Olympic colours to celebrate 8 Years to go to the Brisbane 2032 Olympic and Paralympic Games.
23 July 2024 marks 8 years to the start of the Brisbane 2032 Olympic Games. The Brisbane 2032 Olympic and Paralympic Games will create a legacy that aligns with Council&rsquo;s commitment to making the Brisbane of tomorrow even better than the Brisbane of today.
This Light Up is organised by: Brisbane City Council. &nbsp;

